Second Department,

March, 1961

(March 1, 1961) In the Matter of Gamble Benedict, Appellant. Andre Porumbeanu, Appellant; City Magistrates’ Court of the City of New York, Girls' Term, Respondent.

Motion by the Corporation Counsel of the City of New York to strike appeal from the March Term Calendar, denied.- Nolan, P. J., Ughetta, Christ, Pette and Brennan, JJ., concur.
